    <item>
      <title>亿万富翁萨利纳斯称 1.1 亿美元贷款人是骗子</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-16/ricardo-salinas-debt-billionaire-says-swindler-has-elektra-shares</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥亿万富翁里卡多·萨利纳斯·普利戈 (Ricardo Salinas Pliego) 表示，他已对一起涉嫌数百万美元的欺诈案采取法律行动，该欺诈案导致其旗舰公司的股份落入一名被指控的连环诈骗犯手中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-16/ricardo-salinas-debt-billionaire-says-swindler-has-elektra-shares</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 19:09:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>希尔顿首席执行官乔恩·格雷有望跻身亿万富翁行列</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-16/hilton-ceo-who-gut-checks-jon-gray-is-nearing-billionaire-ranks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[希尔顿全球控股公司 (Hilton Worldwide Holdings Inc.) 对黑石集团 (Blackstone Inc.) 来说是一笔众所周知的好交易，黑石集团利用约 260 亿美元的收购成为了有史以来最成功的杠杆收购之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-16/hilton-ceo-who-gut-checks-jon-gray-is-nearing-billionaire-ranks</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 13:09:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根大通牵头为纽约大厦提供近 12 亿美元融资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-16/jpmorgan-leads-nearly-1-2-billion-financing-for-new-york-towers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通公司和由埃利奥特投资管理公司支持的泰柯资本已为曼哈顿西区的豪华大厦提供了近 12 亿美元的融资。]]></description>
